title: Ghana - Hugh Masekela - Introducting Hedzoleh Soundz (1973)
description:
African music from Ghana Band -- Hedzoleh Soundz


They set up a fantastic groove.  Most of the
tracks are 3/4-6/8 Nanigo Rhythm. 

On top, Hugh Masekela solos.

So, it will not sound like Masekela&#039;s South African
or American Funk grooves either.

1973

This album is out of print.  
I had two vinyl copies I was lending it out so much.

Converted on computer, clicks & pops removed.

192Kbs.  I cannot hear any better than that and
will not be making a lossless version, so
don&#039;t be fussy, just dig the MUSIC and dance!

-------------------------------------------------------------
